ship behaviors.Originality/value: This study provides evidence for integrating ego-identity and social identity theories. In doing so, it bridges developmental psychology literature on personal identity with social and organizational psychology literature on social identity, setting the basis for a comprehensive line of research. © 2013 Springer Science+Business Media New York.
